BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:🌙 Dagens sunnah: Var god mot din granne
DTSTART:20260626T090000
DTEND:20260626T091500
DTSTAMP:20260426T221150Z
UID:sunnah-2026-06-26-var-god-mot-grannen@salattid.se
CATEGORIES:Sunnah,Daglig påminnelse
DESCRIPTION:📖 Hadith\n"Jibreel fortsatte att förmana mig om grannen\, 
 tills jag trodde han skulle göra honom till arvinge."\n— Sahih al-Bukha
 ri 6014\; Sahih Muslim 2624\n\n✨ Att praktisera idag:\n  • Identifiera
  dina tre närmaste grannar — vet du deras namn?\n  • Knacka på idag 
 med en liten gåva: bröd\, dadlar\, kakor\n  • "Granne" inkluderar musl
 im och icke-muslim — inget undantag\n\n───────────
 ─────────\n🇬🇧 English\n"Jibreel kept enjoining goo
 d treatment of the neighbor upon me\, until I thought he would make him an
  heir."\n— Sahih al-Bukhari 6014\; Sahih Muslim 2624\n\nTo practice toda
 y:\n  • Identify your three closest neighbors — do you know their name
 s?\n  • Knock today with a small gift: bread\, dates\, cookies\n  • "N
 eighbor" includes Muslim and non-Muslim — no exceptions\n\n────
 ────────────────\n🕋 العربية (ori
 ginal)\nمَا زَالَ جِبْرِيلُ يُوصِينِي بِالْ
 جَارِ، حَتَّى ظَنَنْتُ أَنَّهُ سَيُوَرِ
 ّثُهُ\n\n────────────────────
 \nSalatTid.se — Sadaqah Jariyah\nhttps://salattid.com/sunnah
